<TITLE> Disband BDR: Ershad </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka Mar 1 (bdnews24.com)Jatiya Party chairman H M Ershad suggests the border force BDR be disbanded "if you call it a mutiny". "According to law, this organisation should be disbanded if you call it a mutiny," the former president said, speaking in parliament Sunday. Recalling one incident, the former army chief said there was mutiny in one of the units of the armed forces and that unit was disbanded. bd
